Business communication workshop CV/LinkedIn workshop Career speed dating workshop Open space technology workshop „The code awakens“ workshop Industry Work Integrated Learning - Disrupting Traditional Education Webpage „ETFMedia“ using WordPress During the course „Business web systems“ we developed a webpage ETFMedia for a marketing agency using WordPress. Information system „Rent a car agency“ Experience as a leader where I worked with my team on different tasks about the information system "Rent a car agency". Information system for „Red Cross“ Created a module Mines with my team as the information system for “Red Cross”. We analyzed everything about mines competitions and all requirements which they need in a system. Application „Online dashboard for professors“ Developed an online dashboard for professors with my team using React.js, and Node.js. Application Auction I was at the position of a full-stack developer at an internship in AtlantBH , where I learned new technologies as Ember.js, Spring Boot and PostgreSQL all of these skills were incorporated in the application Auction. Project “Calculator” using Matlab, MplabX and Microchip16F1939 Created a calculator with my team member using Microchip16F1939, MplabX environment with C programming language and serial communication using Matlab and other features. C and C++ programs, data structures and algorithms Learned object-oriented principles and programming logic using C and C++ programming languages and the advanced programming techniques trough subject „Data structures and algorithms”. Application “Refugees welcome" Designed an application for refugees with my team members where refugees have everything just with the one-click ( accommodation, health care, food …). Betting house using MySql database Created a database for Betting house using Mysql and all knowledge that we learned at the subject “Database fundamentals”.
